window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Two Volumes in a Single Offering!</b></p> <p>Ten years after defeating the Architect and bringing down the System, Sloan Park believed his battle days were over. Settled in a mountain cottage with Sara, he traded godhood for peace, splitting firewood instead of enemy skulls and finding quiet satisfaction in an ordinary life.</p> <p>But when Luther appears with news of a Category Red alert, Sloan's retirement shatters. A new threat tears through Zone 7, something worse than Rifts, spawning white-helmeted Harvesters that transform reality itself. And they're calling Sloan's name.</p> <p>The \"New Dawn Protocol,\" meant to recreate System benefits without its dangers, has instead opened a door to something ancient and hungry from beyond.</p>"; 
